<!--
  ZZZZZ_WakaFoodStatFix - display_value insurance patches (v0.2)

  Why: In the current MO2 mod environment, food tooltips show stats as 0 for
  any food that does not explicitly declare <display_value> tags. vanilla 2.5
  normally falls back to reading <triggered_effect ModifyCVar> values for tooltip
  display, but something in this stack (UI DLL hook or unidentified patch) has
  disturbed that fallback. Injecting static <display_value> tags is the robust
  insurance fix: it forces the tooltip to show values unconditionally.

  Scope (v0.2):
    Section 1 - Medical conditions-altered vanilla foods (8 items)
                DisplayType rewritten to foodCanCoagulants/foodCoagulants
    Section 2 - EFTX Food V2 custom foods (38 items)
                Only triggered_effect, no display_value in source
    Section 3 - Remaining vanilla foods (~61 items)
                Confirmed empirically as also showing 0 stats in this environment
-->
